  Drop obsolete use flags from metadata.xml

*ncview-2.1.2 (15 Jan 2013)

  15 Jan 2013; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org> +ncview-2.1.2.ebuild:
  Version bump

  04 Aug 2012; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org>
  -files/ncview-1.93g-ldflags.patch, -ncview-1.93g.ebuild, ncview-2.1.1.ebuild:
  Removed old. Keyword amd64-linux x86-linux

*ncview-2.1.1 (06 Aug 2011)

  06 Aug 2011; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org> +ncview-2.1.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. Building more standard, now forcing udunits avoiding automagic

  26 Mar 2011; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> -ncview-1.93c.ebuild,
  ncview-1.93g.ebuild, +files/ncview-1.93g-ldflags.patch:
  Link with LDFLAGS, 335387; removed old

  14 Dec 2009; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org> ncview-1.93g.ebuild:
  Fixed ppm support and share/lib issues. Thanks Zak Kipling, bug #272266

